   "id": "title",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Adversarial Patch Experiments — YOLOv8 / YOLO11 / YOLO26\n",
    "\n",
    "**Capstone: Person-Vanishing Adversarial Patch Attack against Ultralytics YOLO**\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook:\n",
    "1. Clones the repo and installs dependencies\n",
    "2. Runs `experiments/ultralytics_patch.py` against YOLOv8n\n",
    "3. Extends to YOLO11n and YOLO26n\n",
    "4. Runs cross-version transfer tests\n",
    "5. Saves all results back to the repo\n",
    "\n",
    "**Before running:** Go to `Runtime > Change runtime type` and select **T4 GPU**."
   ]
  },
  {
