   "source": [
    "## 5. Cross-Version Transfer Tests\n",
    "\n",
    "Core research question: Does a patch trained on YOLOv8 transfer to YOLO11 and YOLO26?\n",
    "This is the primary research contribution that extends Zimoň (2025) to YOLO26."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "transfer-v8-to-v11",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Transfer: patch trained on YOLOv8n, evaluated on YOLO11n\n",
    "!python experiments/ultralytics_patch.py \\\n",
    "    --model yolo11n \\\n",
    "    --eval-only \\\n",
    "    --load-patch outputs/yolov8n_patch_v1/patches/patch.png \\\n",
    "    --display 5"
   ]
